# game/Scenes/CounselorChats/Conversations/cc8.rpy:12
translate russian cc8_6ca8f9d5:

    # pc "Yeah. I'm not sure if I should pursue it or not."
    pc "Да. Я не уверен, стоит ли мне пытаться с ней завязать отношения."

# game/Scenes/CounselorChats/Conversations/cc8.rpy:14
translate russian cc8_14c2691e:

    # sc "Well, my advice would be no."
    sc "Ну, мой совет — нет."

# game/Scenes/CounselorChats/Conversations/cc8.rpy:15
translate russian cc8_4a9ce1c7:

    # sc "There would be a lot of drama, which is never good for your mental health."
    sc "Будет много драмы, а это никогда не идет на пользу твоему психическому здоровью."

# game/Scenes/CounselorChats/Conversations/cc8.rpy:16
translate russian cc8_1a15b947:

    # sc "There's really no good outcome when you put yourself into a situation like that."
    sc "Когда ты попадаешь в такую ситуацию, хорошего исхода не бывает."

# game/Scenes/CounselorChats/Conversations/cc8.rpy:17
translate russian cc8_0b5179eb:

    # pc "But it really seems like she might be interested in me too."
    pc "Но мне действительно кажется, что она тоже может быть мной заинтересована."

# game/Scenes/CounselorChats/Conversations/cc8.rpy:19
translate russian cc8_66109c90:

    # sc "Maybe she is."
    sc "Может быть, и так."

# game/Scenes/CounselorChats/Conversations/cc8.rpy:20
translate russian cc8_7073a90c:

    # sc "Maybe her marriage is not in a good place right now and she sees you as a possible source of happiness."
